verbose_text: Furthermore, in the ipsilateral flocculi, the mRNA expression of GlyR beta was elevated as compared to the contralateral flocculi and the sham operated group at 8 h (P < 0.05 vs. contralateral side; P < 0.05 vs. sham operated group), 1 day (P < 0.01 vs. contra-lateral side; P < 0.01 vs. sham operated group) and 3 days (P < 0.05 vs. contralateral side; P < 0.05 vs. sham operated group) following UL (XREF_FIG).
